text: Shweta Rohidas Jadhav (born 27 December 1985) in a Maharashtrian cricketer.Player's Profile She has played 103 List A and 40 Women's Twenty20 matches. She was a part of India U21 women cricket team that toured Pakistan in season 2005–06.India_Under-21s_Women_in_Pakistan_2005-06 She has played for Maharashtra, Railways, Uttar Pradesh, Central Zone, West Zone. == References == Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Maharashtra women cricketers Category:Uttar Pradesh women cricketers Category:Railways women cricketers Category:Central Zone women cricketers Category:West Zone women cricketers
